                        <layout>
                           <p>Columns: 1;
                                                  ruled lines: 17;
                                                  written lines: 17; Uniform layout. Visible ruling with a mastara. Initial words of each section written in larger characters, preceded with a title page (see e.g. folio 1r, 28r, etc). Catchwords on every verso. The biblical verses are given with punctuation. </p>
